      "span_text": "Immunohistology was performed as described previously. 52 Briefly, OCT-embedded frozen tissue or threedimensional collagen gels were sectioned, and the slides were fixed in 2% paraformaldehyde and permeabilized with for 0.5% Triton X-100 in phosphate-buffered saline (PBS) for 10 minutes at room temperature."
